snippet.title: Pac-Man Battle Royale Chompionship by Bandai Namco Amusements [IAAPA 2021]
snippet.description:
Find out more about this product at: https://primetimeamusements.com/product/pac-man-battle-royale-chompionship/ - A sequel to Pac-Man Battle Royale (2011), this 2022 release takes everything fun about the original and amps it up! Now you have scoring, power-ups and support for up to 8 players. Shipping in April 2022.

PrimeTime Amusements is a global operator, wholesale seller and event renter of brand new and refurbished video arcade machines, simulators, redemption games and more. Based out of Ft. Lauderdale, FL, we have been in business for over 25 years.
